          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Father Agnel School in Noida stands as an esteemed educational institution known for its commitment to holistic learning and character development. Nestled in the vibrant city of Noida, this school boasts state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated faculty that fosters academic excellence, extracurricular participation, and values-driven education. With a rich heritage in nurturing young minds and providing a well-rounded educational experience, Father Agnel School stands as a beacon of quality education, preparing students for the challenges of the modern world while instilling strong moral and ethical values.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
