            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A good school for middle class family students. The school is Christian missionary and there is good discipline maintained. The teachers are good and there is a good academic environment. I as a mother of two children having studied in this school am proud to have such an institution for my children.",
          "publisher": {
